# Project Overview

Tea asset management system (inventory, dashboard, orders).

## Roles

- **admin**: add/edit/delete tea; approve orders (planned)
- **user**: view assets; place orders
- **guest**: view asset list only

## Tech Stack

**Frontend:** React 19, TypeScript 5.9, Vite, Tailwind CSS 4.3

**Backend:** Python, FastAPI, PyMongo, structured JSON logging, centralized API errors

**Database:** MongoDB (email uniqueness, tea filters, text search, orders indexes)

Assume intermediate TypeScript knowledge; explain advanced patterns when used.
